snippet.title: Come Play With Me
snippet.description:
COME PLAY WITH ME is an educational kid friendly toy doll channel featuring parody videos with various characters: Elsa, Anna, Barbie and many more!
Subscribe, it's free and you will know when we upload a new video:)
Thank you for visiting and watching our videos!
